1
00:00:05,675 --> 00:00:06,676
Hey~

2
00:00:06,676 --> 00:00:07,719
Hamin.

3
00:00:07,719 --> 00:00:09,304
You're such a baby.

4
00:00:09,304 --> 00:00:10,347
Can't even drink.

5
00:00:11,014 --> 00:00:12,390
But since you're an adult now,

6
00:00:12,390 --> 00:00:14,017
you need to learn to drink a little for your social life.

7
00:00:16,811 --> 00:00:18,188
How about Hyung pours you a glass?

8
00:00:18,396 --> 00:00:19,564
No, no.

9
00:00:19,564 --> 00:00:21,191
I'm really okay.

10
00:00:21,191 --> 00:00:22,984
Hey, one glass is fine.

11
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:25,695
No Sunbae, I really can't drink.

12
00:00:25,695 --> 00:00:26,988
Here, take it.

13
00:00:27,322 --> 00:00:28,323
Hyung is giving it to you.

14
00:00:28,365 --> 00:00:29,074
Sunbae.

15
00:00:31,034 --> 00:00:32,452
He's really a lightweight.

16
00:00:32,452 --> 00:00:34,454
His face gets red after just one glass,

17
00:00:34,454 --> 00:00:35,872
and he suffers until the next day.

18
00:00:37,958 --> 00:00:39,125
This glass...

19
00:00:39,125 --> 00:00:40,460
I'll take it instead.

20
00:00:43,672 --> 00:00:44,673
Whoa...

21
00:00:44,673 --> 00:00:46,675
Our Taejun is a real man.

22
00:00:46,675 --> 00:00:48,176
You drink it.

23
00:00:54,432 --> 00:00:55,225
Sunbae.

24
00:00:55,725 --> 00:00:57,686
You know the contest you mentioned before?

25
00:00:57,811 --> 00:00:58,353
Yeah.

26
00:00:58,353 --> 00:00:59,145
Want to do it together?

27
00:00:59,854 --> 00:01:01,439
Hey, that's a huge thank you for me.

28
00:01:04,484 --> 00:01:05,527
Are you okay?

29
00:01:05,527 --> 00:01:06,695
If you're uncomfortable, make it obvious.

30
00:01:06,820 --> 00:01:08,613
Just stiffen your face and shake your head.

31
00:01:08,613 --> 00:01:09,781
I'll block them all for you.

32
00:01:09,781 --> 00:01:10,407
Got it?

33
00:01:23,128 --> 00:01:24,671
It's been a while since we all gathered today,

34
00:01:24,671 --> 00:01:25,463
did you have fun?

35
00:01:25,922 --> 00:01:27,590
You looked really uncomfortable.

36
00:01:27,924 --> 00:01:29,467
No, Sunbae.

37
00:01:30,093 --> 00:01:31,678
I was okay thanks to you.

38
00:01:31,678 --> 00:01:33,138
Okay, my foot...

39
00:01:33,138 --> 00:01:35,807
Your face got all red just from drinking Sprite.

40
00:01:38,393 --> 00:01:39,644
Which way is your house?

41
00:01:40,353 --> 00:01:41,604
I...

42
00:01:41,604 --> 00:01:43,732
I just need to go straight that way.

43
00:01:44,441 --> 00:01:45,275
Ah...

44
00:01:46,151 --> 00:01:47,777
It's opposite of mine.

45
00:01:48,236 --> 00:01:49,863
I wanted to walk you home.

46
00:01:49,863 --> 00:01:50,822
That's a shame.

47
00:01:54,451 --> 00:01:55,243
Huh?

48
00:01:57,620 --> 00:01:59,247
Wait, my iPad?

49
00:02:05,128 --> 00:02:06,755
Where did I put my iPad?

50
00:02:06,755 --> 00:02:08,131
I definitely brought it.

51
00:02:09,132 --> 00:02:10,759
Didn't you leave it at the bar?

52
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:11,551
Call them.

53
00:02:11,968 --> 00:02:12,844
Uh, no.

54
00:02:12,844 --> 00:02:14,304
I'm sure before going to the bar,

55
00:02:14,637 --> 00:02:16,431
I packed it at the study room.

56
00:02:17,807 --> 00:02:19,601
I definitely put it in my bag.

57
00:02:20,268 --> 00:02:21,644
Then it's at the study room.

58
00:02:21,644 --> 00:02:22,729
Since we packed up there

59
00:02:22,729 --> 00:02:24,189
and went straight to the bar.

60
00:02:24,898 --> 00:02:26,524
Ah, I guess so...

61
00:02:27,609 --> 00:02:28,526
What should I do.

62
00:02:28,985 --> 00:02:29,736
Let's go check.

63
00:02:30,570 --> 00:02:31,529
Uh, no Hyung.

64
00:02:31,821 --> 00:02:32,781
You must be tired.

65
00:02:33,156 --> 00:02:34,407
I can go by myself.

66
00:02:34,574 --> 00:02:35,366
Forget it.

67
00:02:35,366 --> 00:02:36,534
It's faster if two of us look for it.

68
00:02:36,534 --> 00:02:37,160
Let's hurry.

69
00:02:49,714 --> 00:02:50,840
Ah, found it.

70
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:52,050
It was right here.

71
00:02:52,467 --> 00:02:54,010
It was here, Hyung.

72
00:02:57,138 --> 00:02:58,556
Thank you, Hyung.

73
00:03:15,156 --> 00:03:16,199
Earlier...

74
00:03:17,367 --> 00:03:18,701
I was almost a bit upset.

75
00:03:19,619 --> 00:03:20,370
Excuse me?

76
00:03:22,580 --> 00:03:24,040
When that other guy put his hand on your shoulder,

77
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:24,999
you just stayed still.

78
00:03:28,002 --> 00:03:29,420
I told you to make it obvious if you don't like it.

79
00:03:29,420 --> 00:03:30,922
Why don't you listen to me?

80
00:03:31,714 --> 00:03:33,424
Someone else touching your body...

81
00:03:33,424 --> 00:03:34,759
makes me feel really shitty.

82
00:03:36,845 --> 00:03:37,554
What do you mean...

83
00:03:46,354 --> 00:03:48,314
If you keep making me upset,

84
00:03:49,732 --> 00:03:51,151
you have to be punished.

85
00:04:20,305 --> 00:04:21,556
This is crazy.

86
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,518
This is a dream, a dream.

87
00:04:36,905 --> 00:04:38,740
[Did you get home safely?]

88
00:04:52,295 --> 00:04:54,005
Lee Hamin.

89
00:04:56,507 --> 00:04:58,092
Let's date.

90
00:05:06,684 --> 00:05:09,229
Sunbae, no, I...

91
00:05:09,771 --> 00:05:12,106
I don't swing that way.

92
00:05:16,361 --> 00:05:18,112
Sunbae, you were drunk,

93
00:05:18,112 --> 00:05:20,657
it was a mistake, right?

94
00:05:23,243 --> 00:05:24,285
A mistake?

95
00:05:25,828 --> 00:05:27,205
Just now when we kissed...

96
00:05:27,872 --> 00:05:29,582
what was it when you were grabbing onto my clothes?

97
00:05:32,293 --> 00:05:34,712
That... was just because I was startled.

98
00:05:38,299 --> 00:05:39,676
It's okay.

99
00:05:39,676 --> 00:05:41,302
You don't have to answer right now.

100
00:05:41,886 --> 00:05:43,471
But...

101
00:05:44,389 --> 00:05:46,057
don't even think about running away.

102
00:05:48,726 --> 00:05:50,270
Sunbae, I'm really not like that!

103
00:06:05,493 --> 00:06:09,789
[Ah, and when will you give me my next reward?]
